<l>iṉṟum varuvatu kollō nerunaluṅ</l>
<l>koṉṟatu pōlu nirappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is the poverty that almost killed me yesterday, to meet me today too ?</l>
